Package com.hp.autonomy.hod.client.api.authentication.tokeninformation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationInformation
    Information about the application component of an authentication token.
    ApplicationTokenInformation
    Information about an application token which can be obtained from the get token information API.
    AuthenticationInformation
    Information about the mechanism used to authenticate an entity associated with an authentication token.
    CombinedTokenInformation
    Information about a combined token which can be obtained from the get token information API.
    DeveloperInformation
    Information about the developer component of an authentication token.
    DeveloperTokenInformation
    Information about a developer token which can be obtained from the get token information API.
    GroupInformation
    Information about groups within a particular user store to which users may belong
    UnboundTokenInformation
    Information about an unbound token which can be obtained from the get token information API.
    UserInformation
    Information about the user component of an authentication token.
    UserTokenInformation
    Information about a user token which can be obtained from the get token information API.
